SUB_W10_EVAR_DIVA_LIF_01_000_CUT_000_140.text:
This sounds like a dangerous job;
I cannae swear that I'll be capable
of doing what ye require.

SUB_W10_EVAR_DIVA_CLT_05_000_CUT_000_100.text:
I came here in search of my heart;
I've no interest in whatever cultural
bits and bobs ye may be gathering.

SUB_W10_EVAR_DIVA_CLT_06_050_CUT_000_020.text:
And I'm guessing that's the point behind
all of this. Ye don't care about my heart;
ye just want power.
